Entries.default: "That's been a long time coming. Good work, captain."
"Oh gods, what have we done? What have we done?"
"I hope this does less harm than good. But I don't see it."
"Another nail in the Deadfire's coffin. Who you be planning to nail next?"
"First time I've ever had royal blood on my hands..."
"We've put the Huana at the mercy of Rauatai. I fear we've done a great injustice."
"I don't relish what we've done, but if Rauatai can truly establish peace here, then it was worth it."
